272→
273→| Permission | Type | Default | Enforcement |
274→|------------|------|---------|-------------|
275→| Recipient whitelist | `mapping(address => bool)` | Empty (no one whitelisted) | Revert if `!whitelistedRecipients[recipient]` |
276→| Per-transaction cap | `uint256` | 0 (unlimited) | Revert if `amount > maxPerTransaction && maxPerTransaction != 0` |
277→| Time-windowed limit | `uint256` + `uint256` | 0 (unlimited) | Reset window if expired; revert if `spentInWindow + amount > limit` |
278→| Cooldown | `uint256` | 0 (disabled) | Revert if `block.timestamp < lastClaim + cooldown` |
279→
280→All permissions are independently configurable and default to "no restriction" when set to zero. The whitelist defaults to empty (fully restrictive).
